{"id":312212,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-浙江诸暨市维权人士李小萍替前夫伸冤被/","date":"2013-09-05T22:49:06Z","modified":"2013-09-05T22:49:06Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江诸暨市维权人士李小萍替前夫伸冤被抓（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员黄天怒报道）浙江省诸暨市浣东街道城东村村民李小萍是一位义女。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月她与前夫宣松火曾因故离婚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年宣松火因医疗事故致残，医方推卸责任，法院包庇医方，两次判宣松火败诉，李小萍在现男友的支持下，毅然决然地为前夫伸冤走上了上访申诉之路。李小萍原来是共产党发展的入党对象，因上访被取消了入党资格，并被当地政府送绍兴市精神病医院关押一个月。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span>出于对前妻的信任，宣松火于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日出具了委托李小萍全权处理医疗纠纷上访事宜的委托书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日，浙江省高级法院接受了李小萍的申诉，作出了（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>）浙民申字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1281</span><span>号民事裁定，指令绍兴市中级法院再审。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日，绍兴中院作出了（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>）浙绍民再字第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>号民事判决书，再次判宣松火败诉。昨天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日），李小萍授权《维权网》发表了致习近平、全国人大、最高法院、最高检察院、卫生部、浙江省高院、浙江省检察院和国际人权组织的公开申诉状。今天下午，李小萍和男友徐斌在杭州火车站准备到北京申诉时，被诸暨市“维稳”人员抓捕，晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>点和男友一起被关进诸暨市浣东派出所，现在他们仍被关在派出所，晚饭也没有吃。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>现李小萍向国际社会发出紧急求救。李小萍电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13362589716</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请见：浙江医疗事故受害人宣松火致中国政府及国际社会的申诉状 <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_5.html?spref=tw\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2013/09/blog-post_5.html?spref=tw</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-efwerenKtLw/UiiRBfN6BlI/AAAAAAAAnz0/xRFaTMeHc7M/s1600/11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-efwerenKtLw/UiiRBfN6BlI/AAAAAAAAnz0/xRFaTMeHc7M/s320/11.jpg\" width=\"254\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-elzzXf-DH88/UiiRI8f0m7I/AAAAAAAAn0E/WwSpQ3XMpME/s1600/img135.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-elzzXf-DH88/UiiRI8f0m7I/AAAAAAAAn0E/WwSpQ3XMpME/s320/img135.jpg\" width=\"210\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GzzdwM8OtZg/UiiQU94KCoI/AAAAAAAAnzc/K622bSI1pCQ/s1600/img143.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-GzzdwM8OtZg/UiiQU94KCoI/AAAAAAAAnzc/K622bSI1pCQ/s320/img143.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-STFJcsTD6bI/UiiQaJlOmbI/AAAAAAAAnzk/3A310OxMvBQ/s1600/img145.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-STFJcsTD6bI/UiiQaJlOmbI/AAAAAAAAnzk/3A310OxMvBQ/s320/img145.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-M4xsZkfCc2c/UiiQgk_qeKI/AAAAAAAAnzs/uPmyFiyYUEs/s1600/img275.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-M4xsZkfCc2c/UiiQgk_qeKI/AAAAAAAAnzs/uPmyFiyYUEs/s320/img275.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lH9ecss1MjE/UiiRugBeiCI/AAAAAAAAn0U/LUBeLIG0g8c/s1600/img275_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.